text.tspan: The template is configured to use cm as unit.
To add static objects to your simulation (eg furnitures, etc),
add them as (direct) children of the 'static_objects' layer, and give
them a name (double click on their id in the 'Layers' panel).
Objects whose names start with '_' are ignored.
You can optional add a RDF class after the name, separated with a space.
Objects in the 'dynamic_objects' or 'bg' layers are ignored.
